# 🛒 Next.js E-Commerce Application

A modern and responsive **E-Commerce web application** built with **Next.js** and a **JSON Server mock backend**.  
This project demonstrates real-world front-end architecture, REST API integration, smooth animations, and scalable UI components.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Modern **Next.js App Router** architecture
- Dynamic product and category pages
- Mock backend using **JSON Server**
- RESTful API integration
- Fully responsive design (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- Smooth animations with **Framer Motion**
- Interactive sliders using **Swiper.js**
- Clean and scalable component structure
- Optimized performance and user experience

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

### Frontend
- Next.js
- JavaScript (ES6)
- Tailwind CSS
- CSS

### Backend (Mock)
- JSON Server
- REST APIs

### Libraries & Tools
- Framer Motion
- Swiper.js
- Git & GitHub
- Matrial Ui

